There are interactive panels at the spawn point to change locomotion and movement to be more comfortable; the locomotion panel is different on each platform. Throughout the world, there are signs explaining core VRChat functions, as well as avatars that you can select near a [[Special:MyLanguage/mirror|mirror]] to look at the different avatars, and portals leading to different worlds. One of the highlighted worlds leads to [[Special:MyLanguage/Community:No Time Two Talk|No Time Two Talk]], a social icebreaker game, great for all users. The other portals off to the side lead to curated worlds, and some of the portals may lead to an avatar world for you to find more avatars.